    },
    "body": "Silent payments scanning requires the public key from each eligible input. For P2PKH inputs, the public key is in scriptSig. Access to scriptSig is also needed to identify P2SH-P2WPKH inputs, whose public key is in the witness stack (see #35380).\r\n\r\n`btck_transaction_input_get_script_sig` serializes the scriptSig through `btck_WriteBytes` callback and is exposed on the C++ wrapper as `GetScriptSig()`.",
